{"tid":241367,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"京都現愛國海報 被揭用中國人照片","createTime":"2017-05-13T06:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T08:02:13.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1630e4ae8d9d7be0fb1c51017787231dcf2d658a","tid":241367,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】日本旅遊熱點京都近日出現一批宣傳海報，上面印有一名笑容可掬女子的照片（圖），<span style=\"color: red;\">寫上「我是日本人真是太好了。滿懷自豪地高舉日之丸旗（指日本國旗）吧」，惹來右翼組織宣揚民族主義的質疑。不過，有網民其後發現海報中的女子原來是中國人，有人嘲諷日本愛國主義是「中國製造」，亦有人戲稱海報令人反思何謂日本人。</span><br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本神道教機構神社本廳本周初承認海報為其製作，希望宣揚在國家節日升國旗的做法，教育公眾國家節日的重要性。對於海報中女子本是中國人一事，神社本廳指出海報無明言女子是日本人，所以「沒有問題」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170513/s00014/1494611578186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170513%2Fs00014%2F1494611578186&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69MmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=ef532f43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170513%2Fs00014%2F1494611578186&h=c93f2aca\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170513/s00014/1494611578186</a>"},{"pid":"630de440957bbd31969332134cad6bde21386914","tid":241367,"uid":42875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"換過條友算吧啦仲死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便換埋做大日本帝國國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c20735f7a79386fc9ad11c5d02c196e520e0c6","tid":241367,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"條女唔錯，幾有氣質"},{"pid":"8e1745a1e87664905eee42bf367b8692bfe11440","tid":241367,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dis